%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20totally%20obliterated%20every%20MILITARY%20target%20in%20Iran's%20crown%20jewel%2C%20Kharg%20Island%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Weapons%20are%20the%20most%20powerful%20and%20sophisticated%20that%20the%20World%20has%20ever%20known%20but%2C%20for%20reasons%20of%20decency%2C%20I%20have%20chosen%20NOT%20to%20wipe%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiea-oil-iran-war-historic-disruption-global-energy-markets-trump-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOil%20Infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Island%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20should%20Iran%2C%20or%20anyone%20else%2C%20do%20anything%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20Free%20and%20Safe%20Passage%20of%20Ships%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20I%20will%20immediately%20reconsider%20this%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20continued.%20%26quot%3BIran%20has%20NO%20ability%20to%20defend%20anything%20that%20we%20want%20to%20attack%20%E2%80%94%20There%20is%20nothing%20they%20can%20do%20about%20it!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F116224324444349237%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20CENTCOM%20and%20the%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2228a48db7-289e-4164-aef9-66294f6f4960%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20Kharg%20Island%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKharg%20Island%20is%20a%20small%20island%20in%20the%20Persian%20Gulf%2C%20located%20roughly%20300%20miles%20from%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20which%20is%20known%20for%20its%20signi