not%20humanoid%20designs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAtoms%20is%20acquiring%20Pronto%2C%20an%20autonomous%20vehicle%20startup%20founded%20by%20Anthony%20Levandowski.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Uber%20CEO%20is%20venturing%20into%20robotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcloud-kitchens-travis-kalanick-san-francisco-location-address-pictures-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETravis%20Kalanick%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20that%20Atoms%20is%20out%20of%20stealth%20mode%20and%20expanding%20beyond%20food%20delivery%20infrastructure%20into%20industries%20such%20as%20food%20service%2C%20mining%2C%20and%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-Uber%20CEO%20published%20a%201%2C600-plus%20word%20manifesto%20of%20his%20company%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20told%20my%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20and%20colleagues%20about%20my%20plans%20for%20what%20was%20next%2C%20they%20were%20really%20excited%20that%20I%20was%20'coming%20back%2C'%26quot%3B%20Kalanick%20wrote%20on%20the%20website%20for%20the%20new%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20is%2C%20I%20never%20left.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20a%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20on%20%26quot%3BTBPN%26quot%3B%20on%20Friday%2C%20Kalanick%20told%20show%20hosts%20%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3EJohn%20Coogan%20and%20Jordi%20Hays%20that%20he%20will%20be%20%3C%2Fmark%3Efolding%20his%20ghost-kitchen%20startup%20CloudKitchens%20into%20the%20new%20venture%2C%20a%20detail%20that%20is%20also%20mentioned%20on%20Atoms'%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAtoms'%20webpage%20says%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20%26quot%3Bwheelbase%20for%20robots%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20platform%20designed%20to%20power%20specialized%20machines%20rather%20than%20humanoid%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Atoms%20we%20make%20gainfully%20employed%20robots%20%E2%80%94%20specialized%20robots%20with%20productive%20jobs%20that%20bring%20abundance%20to%20their%20owners%20and%20society%20at%20large%2C%26quot%3B%20Kalanick%20wrote%20on%20the%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20said%20on%20%26quot%3BTBPN%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20company%20will%20focus%20on%20practical%20industrial%20systems%20instead%20of%20humanlike%20designs%2C%20and%20that%20the%20venture%20was%20just%20renamed%20as%20%26quot%3BAtoms%26quot%3B%20from%20%26quot%3BCity%20Storage%20Systems%26quot%3B%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20in%20stealth%20mode%20for%20eight%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kalanick.%20%26quot%3BEmployees%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20put%20the%20name%20of%20the%20company%20on%20their%20LinkedIn.%20We%20have%20thousands%20of%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHumanoids%20have%20their%20place%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20room%20for%20specialized%20robots%20that%20do%20things%20in%20an%20efficient%2C%20sort%20of%20industrial-scale%20kind%20of%20way%2C%20which%20is%20sort%20of%20where%20we%20play%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kalanick%2C%20Atoms%20is%20close%20to%20acquiring%20Pronto%2C%20an%20autonomous-vehicle%20startup%20focused%20on%20industrial%20and%20mining%20sites%2C%20founded%20by%20his%20former%20Uber%20colleague%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-google-engineer-pardoned-donald-trump-anthony-levandowski-ai-church-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthony%20Levandowski%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick's%20partnership%20with%20Levandowski%20would%20be%20the%20reunion%20of%20two%20of%20the%20most%20infamous%20Uber%20alums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevandowski%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ceo-travis-kalanick-life-rise-and-fall-photos-resigned-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKalanick%20co-founded%20Uber%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202009%20and%20was%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ceo-travis-kalanick-out-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20until%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20he%20resigned%20after%20facing%20immense%20investor%20pressure%20stemming%20from%20reports%20of%20a%20toxic%20work%20culture%20and%20multiple%20clashes%20with%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevandowski%2C%20an%20alum%20of%20Google's%20self-driving%20project%20that%20is%20now%20Waymo%2C%20was%20brought%20into%20Uber%20in%202016%20after%20the%20ride-hailing%20giant%20bought%20his%20autonomous%20trucking%20outfit%2C%20Otto.%20In%20less%20than%20a%20year%2C%20he%20was%20fired%20from%20the%20company%20after%20Google%20sued%20Uber%2C%20accusing%20Levandowski%20of%20stealing%20trade%20secrets%20from%20the%20self-driving%20project.%20Uber%20settled%20with%20Waymo%2C%20but%20Levandowski%20was%20convicted%20in%20a%20separate%20criminal%20case%20in%202020%20of%20one%20count%20of%20trade%20secret%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevandowski%20was%20later%20pardoned%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20before%20he%20even%20began%20serving%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthony-levandowski-waymo-uber-sentencing-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E18-month%20prison%20sentence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick's%20manifesto%20doesn't%20explicitly%20mention%20a%20robotaxi%20venture%20%E2%80%94%20only%20that%20one%20of%20Atom's%20portfolio%20will%20include%20%26quot%3Btransport%20industries.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20writes%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20age%26quot%3B%20of%20abundance%20in%20which%20manufacturing%20is%20autonomous%20and%20the%20cars%20that%20are%20built%20by%20robots%20can%20drive%20themselves%2C%20referencing%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20the%20full%20manifesto%20below%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EVision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20left%20Uber%20in%202017%20heartbroken.%20I%20had%20been%20torn%20away%20from%20an%20idea%20and%20a%20movement%20that%20I%20had%20poured%20my%20life%20into.%20I%20had%20lost%20my%20bearings%20as%20I%20found%20the%20world%20increasingly%20operating%20by%20the%20rules%20of%20perception%20not%20reality.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIt%20was%20only%20days%20after%20the%20death%20of%20my%20mother%20and%20the%20near%20death%20of%20my%20father%20in%20a%20boating%20accident%20when%20an%20investor%20decided%20to%20come%20out%20from%20the%20shadows%20and%20exploit%20this%20vulnerable%20moment%20to%20wrestle%20control%20of%20this%20idea%20away.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20bled%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20perish.%20I%20got%20back%20up%20and%20fought%20my%20way%20back%20into%20the%20arena%2C%20back%20to%20my%20calling.%20Back%20to%20building.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EDigitizing%20the%20Physical%20World%20is%20my%20life's%20work.%20After%20Uber%20I%20started%20building%20City%20Storage%20Systems.%20The%20obscure%20name%20was%20a%20nod%20to%20Atoms-based%20computation%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20Real%20Estate.%20Our%20first%20computer%20was%20a%20Food%20computer%20-%20digitized%20manufacturing%2C%20real%20estate%20and%20logistics%20for%20food.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EToday%20we%20expand%20our%20physical%20world%20computation%20portfolio%20to%20the%20Mining%20and%20Transport%20industries%20and%20rename%20the%20company%20%3Cstrong%3EAtoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22163873d3-ed60-4974-9db7-60097c7007f6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAtoms%20Mission%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E01%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EPhysical%20automation%20to%20transform%20industry%20and%20move%20the%20world%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225cd6bb0b-9822-4ea3-a6b5-81e28dd7c07b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20Computers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E02%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAtoms%20Food%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EInfrastructure%20for%20better%20food.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAtoms%20Mining%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMore%20productive%20mines%20to%20power%20earth's%20industries.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAtoms%20Transport%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWheelbase%20for%20robots.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3EAt%20Atoms%20we%20make%20%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3Egainfully%20employed%20robots%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%94%20specialized%20robots%20with%20productive%20jobs%20that%20bring%20abundance%20to%20their%20owners%20and%20society%20at%20large.%20I'm%20excited%20to%20share%20more%20about%20our%20vision%20for%20Atoms%20below.%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226dddec07-86bc-47d3-a948-76790a66cced%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EValuable%20Unknown%20Truths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E03%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIn%20the%20battle%20against%20entropy%2C%20humans%20optimize%20for%20finding%20valuable%20unknown%20truths.%20Because%20when%20you%20are%20good%20at%20discovering%20valuable%20unknown%20truths%2C%20you%20know%20things%20others%20don't%20know.%20And%20when%20you%20are%20good%20at%20knowing%20things%20others%20don't%2C%20you%20can%20do%20things%20that%20others%20can't.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAn%20organization%20of%20valuable%20unknown%20truth%20seeking%20is%20able%20to%20do%20more%20and%20more%20things%20that%20others%20can't%20do.%20That%20organization%20will%20find%20that%20it%20can%20bring%20change%20and%20progress%20at%20accelerating%20speeds%2C%20faster%20and%20faster%20as%20its%20knowledge%20advantage%20grows.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThat%20change%20is%20God's%20work%20-%20human%20progress%20in%20service%20to%20the%20battle%20against%20entropy%2C%20dust%2C%20and%20death.%20Civilization.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22232180a7-f180-4218-b5be-e409dbe7a34d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPast%20is%20Prologue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E04%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EHuman%20history%20is%20the%20recording%20of%20this%20fight%20and%20the%20advance%20of%20civilization.%20From%20basic%20tools%20for%20survival%20to%20levered%20machinery%20that%20humans%20operate%20as%20industry%20emerged.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ESoftware%20has%20automated%20tasks%20of%20language%20and%20math%2C%20but%20the%20complete%20automation%20of%20the%20physical%20world%20%E2%80%94%20autonomy%20%E2%80%94%20remains%20largely%20untouched%20territory%2C%20the%20principal%20unlock%20to%20the%20next%20era%20of%20progress%20and%20abundance.%20History%20refers%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20moment%20of%20radical%20progress%20as%20a%20Golden%20Age.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EEverything%20in%20our%20world%2C%20in%20our%20cities%2C%20in%20our%20civilization%20%E2%80%94%20look%20around%20you%20%E2%80%94%20is%20mined%20or%20grown%20%E2%80%94%20manufactured%20and%20moved.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20next%20Golden%20Age%20will%20be%20upon%20us%20when%20the%20means%20of%20growing%2C%20mining%2C%20manufacturing%20and%20moving%20physical%20things%20becomes%20fully%20divorced%20from%20human%20labor.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22114aa187-b077-42eb-b24b-231577f4419e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbundance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E05%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhy%20a%20Golden%20Age%3F%20Because%20when%20the%20means%20to%20make%20and%20move%20is%20reduced%20to%20computation%2C%20minerals%20and%20energy%20alone%2C%20when%20the%20machines%20that%20make%20machines%20that%20make%20things%20are%20also%20autonomous%2C%20the%20organization%20of%20human%20capital%20becomes%20superhuman.%20Efficiency%20and%20value%20emerges%20via%20self-improving%20software%20while%20we%20sleep.%20The%20ability%20to%20produce%20at%20an%20unfathomably%20large%20scale%20is%20the%20only%20logical%20result.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhen%20Tesla%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Blights%20out%26quot%3B%20manufacturing%20plant%20and%20the%20raw%20materials%20are%20brought%20in%20by%20autonomous%20Tesla%20freight%20vehicles%2C%20and%20the%20manufactured%20cars%20then%20autonomously%20travel%20to%20their%20new%20owners'%20homes%E2%80%A6what%20will%20that%20cost%3F%20It%20will%20simply%20be%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20raw%20materials%20and%20the%20energy%20to%20produce%20the%20final%20product.%20And%20what%20about%20when%20Amazon%20warehouses%20are%20autonomous%2C%20and%20supplied%20by%20autonomous%20manufacturers%20of%20the%20goods%20they%20sell%2C%20and%20the%20goods%20delivered%20by%20autonomous%20delivery%20vehicles%20to%20your%20home%3F%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca00dcaf-1322-447b-8f6c-693c01263023%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Inevitable%20Destination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E06%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20Golden%20Age%20is%20close%20at%20hand%20but%20the%20journey%20ahead%20still%20has%20its%20challenges.%20Physical%20world%20autonomy%20requires%20AI%20for%20the%20physical%20world.%20This%20kind%20of%20intelligence%20requires%20computation%20we%20haven't%20invented%2C%20at%20an%20efficiency%20we%20can't%20yet%20fathom%20with%20deep%20learning%20models%20to%20understand%20and%20act%20in%20the%20physical%20world%20that%20don't%20yet%20exist.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EBut%20Moore's%20law%20(squared)%20is%20our%20friend.%20The%20cost%20per%20unit%20of%20intelligence%20is%20going%20down%20in%20price%20by%2090%25%20per%20year.%20Total%20capabilities%20and%20general%20intelligence%20have%20increased%20nearly%201000-fold%20over%20the%20last%203%20years.%20Hardware%2C%20software%20and%20manufacturing%20productivity%20will%20continue%20to%20compound%20each%20other%20to%20ever%20increasing%20speeds%20of%20progress.%20Though%20we're%20less%20than%20one%20millionth%20of%20the%20way%20there%2C%20the%20inevitable%20destination%20is%20the%20singularity%20%E2%80%94%20superhuman%20intelligence%20and%20efficiency.%20Until%20then%2C%20Abundance%20will%20be%20creating%20more%20jobs%2C%20not%20less.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22397110c3-9f8b-4c76-b39c-b6556490da46%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELand%20and%20Expand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E07%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhere%20do%20the%20materials%20and%20minerals%20come%20from%3F%20Where%20do%20we%20manufacture%3F%20Where%20do%20we%20harvest%20and%20store%20energy%3F%20Land%20as%20a%20critical%20resource%20and%20the%20competency%20of%20real%20estate%20development%20of%20that%20land%20are%20dramatically%20underappreciated%20ingredients%20for%20Physical%20world%20AI.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EProducing%20more%20minerals%20that%20power%20the%20chemistry%20for%20state%20change%20and%20the%20materials%20for%20machines%20to%20manufacture%20will%20be%20an%20urgent%20imperative.%20Acquiring%20and%20developing%20the%20land%20that%20produces%20these%20minerals%20and%20materials%20is%20a%20critical%20competency.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fb818cf-e904-4d6c-a604-d0f01019619e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDigitizing%20the%20Physical%20World%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E08%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EOnce%20you%20have%20the%20materials%20and%20energy%20for%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20%26quot%3Bprogress%20machines%26quot%3B%2C%20what%20kinds%20of%20machines%20are%20they%20and%20what%20do%20these%20machines%20do%3F%20The%20imperative%20is%20movement%20and%20action%20in%20the%20physical%20world%20with%20a%20software-like%20perspective%20on%20physical%20automation%20%E2%80%94%20think%20of%20it%20as%20treating%20atoms%20like%20bits%20or%20what%20we%20like%20to%20call%20Digitizing%20the%20Physical%20World.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIt%20means%20approaching%20physical%20world%20problems%20like%20software%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20building%20atoms-based%20computers.%20The%20core%20computing%20resources%3A%20CPU%2C%20Storage%2C%20Network%20for%20the%20physical%20world%20%E2%80%94%20digitized%20manufacturing%2C%20real%20estate%20and%20transport.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI'll%20use%20an%20old%20Uber%20analogy%20to%20bring%20this%20framework%20to%20life.%20In%20any%20given%20city%2C%20Uber%20has%2010's%20of%20thousands%20of%20sensors%20on%20the%20road.%20Those%20sensors%20are%20the%20uber%20drivers'%20phones.%20Those%20phones%20track%20the%20exact%20location%20and%20movement%20of%20Uber%20vehicles%20in%20the%20city.%20Because%20of%20how%20they%20move%2C%20Uber%20should%20know%20the%20real-time%20state%20of%20every%20traffic%20light%20in%20the%20city%20and%20could%20even%20know%20where%20most%20of%20the%20trash-trucks%20are%20at%20any%20given%20moment%20-%20ubers%20also%20get%20stuck%20behind%20trash%20trucks.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ENow%20when%20you%20request%20a%20ride%2C%20Uber%20can%20dispatch%20to%20any%20nearby%20Uber%20vehicle%20(Step%201.)%2C%20but%20it%20should%20be%20able%20to%20predict%20which%20vehicle%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20stuck%20behind%20a%20trash%20truck%2C%20or%20which%20vehicle%20might%20get%20in%20a%20bad%20traffic%20light%20cycle%20on%20its%20way%20to%20picking%20you%20up%20(Step%201%20and%20Step%202.).%20Maybe%20it%20should%20dispatch%20to%20a%20car%20but%20route%20that%20car%20around%20the%20trash%20truck%20so%20that%20it%20can%20get%20to%20you%203%20minutes%20faster%20(Step%203)%3F%20The%20car%20gets%20to%20you%20faster%2C%20you%20get%20to%20the%20destination%20faster%2C%20and%20Uber%20became%20a%20mini-time-machine%20because%20it%20effectively%20digitized%20the%20physical%20world.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296e4876b-93e4-4197-a3c2-fbefa90f9cc6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3-steps%20for%20Digitizing%20the%20Physical%20World%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3Estep%2001%3A%20Understand%20the%20current%20state%20of%20the%20physical%20world.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3Estep%2002%3A%20Predict%20the%20future%20state%20of%20the%20physical%20world.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3Estep%2003%3A%20Control%20the%20future%20state%20of%20the%20physical%20world.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThis%20framework%20applies%20to%20most%20things%20that%20move%20and%20act%20in%20our%20cities.%20The%20efficiency%20gained%2C%20the%20time%20saved%2C%20the%20value%20created%20is%20the%20upside%20of%20the%20progress%20machines%20that%20digitize%20the%20physical%20world.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229cf604a-6fb0-4fbf-90de-0f71fcca9dc4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Physical%20AI%20Tech%20Stack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E09%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20tech%20stack%20for%20industrial%20progress%20machines%20is%20not%20for%20the%20faint%20of%20heart.%20The%20Physical%20AI%20tech%20stack%20is%20daunting.%20It%20requires%20a%20polymath%20organization%20spanning%20many%20domains%20from%20sensors%20and%20compute%20to%20manufacturing%2C%20chemistry%20and%20real%20estate.%20No%20single%20company%20has%20to%20do%20it%20all%2C%20but%20the%20more%20cross%20stack%20competence%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20that%20company%20can%20earn%20its%20keep.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2Sensors%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2Compute%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2AI%20Models%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2Manipulation%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2Software%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2Ops%20research%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2Manufacturing%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2Real%20estate%20construction%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2Energy%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%A2Chemistry%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c630571d-2dfb-490e-be35-d70960023da8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGainfully%20Employed%20Robots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E10%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20critical%20early%20decision%20in%20Physical%20AI%3A%20should%20you%20make%20generalized%20robots%20or%20specialized%20ones%3F%20To%20humanoid%20or%20not%20to%20humanoid%2C%20that%20is%20the%20question.%20Humanoids%20will%20handle%20a%20large%20diversity%20of%20tasks%20with%20an%20anthropomorphic%20design.%20Good%20for%20low%20scale%20tasks%20in%20bespoke%20human-designed%20spaces.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EA%20robotic%20housekeeper%20needs%20to%20vacuum%2C%20dust%2C%20fold%20clothes%2C%20wash%20dishes%2C%20throw%20away%20trash%2C%20clean%20toilets%2C%20put%20objects%20back%20in%20their%20place.%20A%20huge%20diversity%20of%20low%20volume%20tasks%2C%20where%20everyone's%20home%20has%20a%20bespoke%20design%20and%20inconvenient%20architecture%20(e.g.%20stairs).%20This%20is%20a%20humanoid's%20job.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EBut%20what%20if%20you%20had%20an%20industrial%20kitchen%20and%20needed%20to%20make%201000%20pancakes%20an%20hour%3F%20I%20couldn't%20think%20of%20a%20worse%20approach%20than%20a%20humanoid.%20A%20specialized%20machine%20that%20makes%20pancake%20batter%20at%20a%20large%20scale%2C%20with%20a%20heated%20iron%20apparatus%20that%20can%20cook%20100%20pancakes%20at%20a%20time%20to%20golden%20brown%20perfection.%20No%20awkward%20robotic%20arm%20flipping%20pancakes%20%E2%80%94%20instead%2C%20precision%20cooking%2C%20ultra-speed%20and%20throughput%2C%20efficient%20use%20of%20space%20designed%20for%20the%20machine.%20This%20is%20where%20specialized%20robotics%20shine.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EBuilders%20need%20to%20be%20careful%20of%20the%20human%20fascination%20with%20seeing%20mechanized%20versions%20of%20us.%20Every%20humanoid%20demo%20or%20launch%20in%20recent%20memory%20usually%20starts%20with%20a%20humanoid%20dance%20show%20or%20martial%20arts%20display.%20The%20recent%20humanoid%20Olympics%20in%20Beijing%20highlighted%20many%20advances%20in%20humanoid%20development.%20I%20watched%20the%20half-marathon%20and%20couldn't%20help%20but%20think%20how%20much%20better%20it%20would%20be%20if%20they%20just%20had%20wheels.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EGainfully%20employed%20robots%20are%20the%20machines%20best%20suited%20for%20the%20job%20at%20hand%2C%20that%20can%20make%20a%20living%20doing%20it.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222801b5ca-f29f-43e9-ba6c-774bcae0c342%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20Back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E11%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20often%20get%20the%20question%20from%20entrepreneurs%20or%20executives%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20should%20I%20do%20next%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMy%20answer%20has%20always%20been%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20deeply%20self%20aware%20and%20when%20the%20right%20thing%20comes%2C%20you%20will%20know%20it.%20If%20you%20know%20yourself%2C%20your%20next%20thing%2C%20your%20new%20idea%2C%20your%20work%20soulmate%20will%20reveal%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhen%20I%20told%20my%20friends%2C%20family%20and%20colleagues%20about%20my%20plans%20for%20what%20was%20next%2C%20they%20were%20really%20excited%20that%20I%20was%20%26quot%3Bcoming%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20thing%20is%2C%20I%20never%20left.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kalanick-ex-uber-misfits-entering-robotics-game-atoms-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773439000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b476674d65ec51752a01af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kalanick-ex-uber-misfits-entering-robotics-game-atoms-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20CEO%20of%20Uber%2C%20Travis%20Kalanick%2C%20unveils%20a%20venture%20that%20is%20previously%20in%20stealth%20mode%2C%20aiming%20to%20build%20a%20%26quot%3Bwheelbase%20for%20robots.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li%2CAlex%20Bitter%2CLloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engage