20of%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMake%20partners%20prove%20the%20value%20of%20AI%20tools%20they're%20providing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20woman%20with%20glasses%20speaking%20into%20a%20microphone%20at%20a%20formal%20dinner%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b30ba74d65ec517529ebde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224893%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BYour%20shareholders%2C%20your%20leaders%20are%20(asking)%2C%20'What's%20the%20big%20revolutionary%20bang%20that's%20gonna%20unlock%20our%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Roz%20Harris%2C%20VP%20Talent%2C%20Zillow.%3Cp%3ENero%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoz%20Harris%2C%20VP%2C%20Talent%2C%20Zillow%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPut%20the%20pressure%20on%20your%20product%20partners%2C%20the%20vendors%20that%20you're%20using%2C%20to%20justify%20their%20roadmaps%20and%20why%20they're%20getting%20your%20dollar.%20Because%20your%20shareholders%2C%20your%20leaders%20are%20(asking)%2C%20'What's%20the%20big%20revolutionary%20bang%20that's%20going%20to%20unlock%20our%20teams%3F%20That's%20going%20to%20unlock%20the%20business%2C%20going%20to%20move%20things%20forward%3F'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20promise%20you%20many%20of%20us%20aren't%20companies%20that%20are%20going%20to%20build%20that%20thing%20ourselves.%20But%20we%20do%20have%20product%20partners%20who%20should%20be%20enabling%20us%20to%20do%20those%20things.%20But%20are%20we%20articulating%20our%20needs%20to%20them%3F%20Are%20we%20articulating%20those%20well%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompany-wide%20hackathons%20allow%20employees%20to%20shine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Profile%20view%20of%20woman%20at%20formal%20dinner%20speaking%20into%20a%20microphone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b30a83a7a4f9df67ba4056%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5