ution%2C%20and%20are%20sprouting%20all%20over%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20can%20also%20be%20a%20drain%20on%20water%20and%20energy%2C%20and%20face%20opposition%20in%20many%20towns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20survey%20found%20that%20Americans%20who%20know%20about%20data%20centers%20don't%20like%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C200%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20scattered%20across%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20thanks%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fso-much-money-that-its-hard-for-to-keep-up-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20boom%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20many%20more%20are%20on%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20data%20centers%20also%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20confirm%20the%20adage%20%26quot%3Bfamiliarity%20breeds%20contempt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20survey%20from%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Council%2C%20conducted%20in%20January%20and%20published%20Thursday%2C%20found%20that%20the%20more%20Americans%20learn%20about%20data%20centers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20effects%20on%20home%20energy%20costs%2C%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20the%20environment%2C%20local%20jobs%2C%20and%20tax%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20the%20more%20cynical%20they%20feel%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo-thirds%20of%20adults%20who%20have%20heard%20a%20lot%20about%20data%20centers%20say%20they're%20mostly%20bad%20for%20home%20energy%20costs%2C%20compared%20with%2042%25%20of%20those%20who%20have%20heard%20a%20little%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20center%20reported.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2063%25%20of%20those%20who%20have%20heard%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20facilities%20say%20they're%20mostly%20bad%20for%20the%20environment%2C%20compared%20with%2048%25%20of%20those%20who%20have%20heard%20a%20little.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPew%20found%20that%2025%25%20of%20adults%20know%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%26quot%3B%20about%20data%20centers%2C%20while%2050%25%20said%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%26quot%3B%20and%2025%25%20said%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%20It%20surveyed%208%2C500%20Americans%20for%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20data%20centers%20have%20been%20around%20for%20decades%2C%20their%20numbers%20are%20skyrocketing%20as%20companies%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20others%20race%20to%20develop%20ever%20more%20intelligent%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20like%20Oracle%2C%20for%20example%2C%20will%20invest%20%24500%20billion%20over%20four%20years%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-openai-stargate-loans-jpmorgan-diminishing-interest-debt-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20infrastructure%20for%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20venture%20called%20Stargate%2C%20which%20is%20backed%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20The%20president%20has%20made%20data%20center%20construction%20a%20key%20pillar%20of%20his%20administration's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-ai-stargate-openai-oracle-softbank-technology-investment-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrategy%20to%20defeat%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20race%20to%20develop%20advanced%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Americans%20outside%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20however%2C%20feel%20as%20excited%20about%20another%20new%20data%20center%20as%20they%20do%20about%20AI%20overall.%20Some%20communities%20are%20now%20pushing%20back%2C%20citing%20concerns%20about%20energy%20costs%20and%20the%20environment.%20Tensions%20have%20flared%20at%20protests%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-meeting-claremore-oklahoma-man-arrested-beale-infrastructure-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecity%20hall%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericas-hottest-nimby-issue-data-centers-sanders-desantis-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECapitol%20Hill%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20these%20growing%20concerns%2C%20tech%20leaders%20said%20this%20month%20they%20would%20cover%20a%20greater%20share%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-data-centers-electricity-donald-trump-ratepayer-protection-pledge-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20center%20energy%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20be%20making%20their%20own%20electricity%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20of%20the%20tech%20companies.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20going%20to%20be%20taking%20from%20the%20grid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20companies%20signed%20a%20%26quot%3Bpledge%26quot%3B%20to%20provide%20their%20own%20power%2C%20which%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20is%20voluntary%20and%20includes%20no%20repercussions%20if%20they%20don't%20comply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-construction-ai-environment-backlash-pew-research-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773425328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b43bb44d65ec517529f988%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-construction-ai-environment-backlash-pew-research-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Data%20centers%20power%20the%20AI%20revolution%2C%20and%20are%20sprouting%20all%20over%20the%20US.%20They%20can%20also%20drain%20water%20and%20energy%2C%20and%20face%20growing%20opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-construction-ai-environment-backlash-pew-research-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Charts%20show%20how%20the%20Iran%20war%20has%20pushed%20ticket%20prices%20sharply%20higher%20on%203%20major%20US%20airline%20routes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20departure%20gate%20of%20Terminal%201%20at%20JFK%20International%20Airport%20is%20seen%20in%20New%20York%20on%20August%2015%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b442d9a96e437d6eb848d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDelta%20Air%20Lines'%20service%20from%20New%20York's%20JFK%20Airport%20(pictured)%20to%20London%20Heathrow%20is%20up%20from%20%24285%20to%20%24553%20over%20a%20month.%3Cp%3ECHARLY%20TRIBALLEAU%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWar%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20has%20pushed%20fuel%20costs%2C%20and%20therefore%20airfares%2C%20sharply%20higher.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20charted%20the%20increase%20in%20ticket%20prices%20for%20three%20major%20flight%20paths%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFares%20from%20New%20York%20to%20LA%2C%20New%20York%20to%20London%2C%20and%20from%20the%20US%20mainland%20to%20the%20Caribbean%20have%20jumped.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20next%20flight%20could%20be%20twice%20as%20expensive%20because%20the%20Iran%20war%20is%20causing%20volatility%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-inflation-iran-trump-iea-imf-chief-economist-hormuz-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20crude%20is%20up%20more%20than%2050%25%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%20to%20around%20%24101%20a%20barrel.%20Jet%20fuel%20costs%20are%20rising%20faster.%20The%20Argus%20US%20Jet%20Fuel%20Index%20is%20up%2072%25%20over%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20spells%20difficulty%20for%20airlines%20because%20jet%20fuel%20is%20typically%20their%20biggest%20expense%20after%20labor.%20While%20many%20airlines%20around%20the%20world%20hedge%20against%20fuel%20costs%2C%20most%20American%20ones%20do%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20data%20from%20Deutsche%20Bank%2C%20Business%20Insider%20charted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-raise-prices-cancel-flights-due-to-fuel-costs-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erising%20airfares%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20three%20major%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20looks%20at%20the%20lowest%20available%20published%20fares%2021%20days%20in%20advance%20of%20the%20flights.%20The%20published%20fare%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20a%20ticket%20has%20been%20purchased%20for%20that%20amount%2C%20the%20Deutsche%20Bank%20research%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECross-country%20flights%2C%20often%20known%20in%20the%20industry%20as%20transcontinental%20flights%2C%20have%20seen%20the%20biggest%20week-over-week%20spike%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20double%2C%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20is%20the%20country's%20busiest%20domestic%20route%2C%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%203.4%20million%20seats%20out%20of%20JFK%20Airport%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20OAG%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FpD9hK%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20line%20chart%20shows%20the%20prices%20of%20airfares%20between%20February%2027%20and%20March%2027%20for%20transcontinental%20flights%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FpD9hK%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20price%20of%20a%20transcontinental%20flight%20has%20risen%20from%20%24167%20to%20%24414%2C%20Deutsche%20Bank's%20analysis%20showed.%20In%20the%20past%20week%2C%20the%20average%20has%20spiked%20107%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20Airlines%20is%20offering%20flights%20from%20Washington%20Dulles%20Airport%20to%20San%20Francisco%20for%20%24502%2C%20up%20from%20%24149%20a%20month%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternational%20business%20travellers%20are%20also%20seeing%20flight%20prices%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-airways-new-york-london-flight-first-class-upgrade-review-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20to%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20country's%20most%20popular%20international%20route%2C%20and%20the%2010th-busiest%20in%20the%20world.%20Nearly%204%20million%20seats%20were%20scheduled%20on%20flights%20between%20JFK%20and%20Heathrow%20last%20year%2C%20per%20OAG.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FbtcAz%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20line%20chart%20shows%20the%20prices%20of%20airfares%20between%20February%2027%20and%20March%2027%20for%20flights%20from%20New%20York%20to%20London%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FbtcAz%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20average%20Transatlantic%20flight%20is%20some%2040%25%20more%20expensive%20than%20a%20month%20ago%2C%20there%20are%20bigger%20rises%20for%20the%20New%20York-London%20route.%20However%2C%20it%20also%20appears%20more%20volatile%20here%20with%20a%20big%20dip%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20Air%20Lines'%20service%20is%20up%20from%20%24285%20to%20%24553%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%20while%20United's%20is%20up%20to%20%24846.%20That's%20a%20177%25%20rise%20compared%20to%20a%20week%20earlier%2C%20according%20to%20Deutsche%20Bank's%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20bad%20news%20for%20vacationers%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaps-show-sc