%3A1773423420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F26%2F03%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-ethiopia-landslides_7191549.jpg%3F20260313174416%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fat-least-80-killed-and-many-more-missing-after-deadly-landslides-in-ethiopia-13519323%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20days%20of%20mourning%20have%20been%20declared%20in%20Ethiopia%20after%2080%20people%20died%20in%20landslides%20triggered%20by%20heavy%20flooding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fat-least-80-killed-and-many-more-missing-after-deadly-landslides-in-ethiopia-13519323%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20a%20computer%20science%20grad%2C%20she%20was%20promised%20stability.%20Then%20AI%20arrived.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223279%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kiran%20Maya%20Sheikh%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b42edea7a4f9df67ba4c84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222721%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESoftware%20engineer%20Kiran%20Maya%20Sheikh%3Cp%3EKiran%20Maya%20Sheikh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20version%20of%20this%20story%20originally%20appeared%20in%20the%20BI%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESign%20up%20for%20the%20weekly%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20Fridays%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20feeling%20smug.%20I'd%20just%20sent%20another%20Tech%20Memo%20edition%20telling%20subscribers%20to%20stop%20worrying%20about%20AI%20eating%20tech%20jobs%20because%20Anthropic%2C%20the%20leading%20AI%20company%20pushing%20this%20narrative%2C%20is%20hiring%20so%20many%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20clever!%20Until%20I%20got%20an%20email%20from%20a%20reader%2C%20Kiran%20Maya%20Sheikh.%20She%20has%20a%20computer%20science%20degree%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Irvine.%20It's%20a%20great%20school%2C%20and%20she%20graduated%20with%20an%20impressive%20GPA.%20And%20yet%2C%20she's%20struggling%20to%20land%20that%20all-important%20first%20full-time%20software%20engineering%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20bad%20advice%20to%20'not%20worry%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20causing%20disruption%20in%20this%20job%20market.%20Employers%20are%20prioritizing%20hiring%20experienced%20workers%2C%20but%20not%20new%20graduates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20I%20interviewed%20Kiran%20for%20Tech%20Memo.%20It%20was%20an%20eye-opening%20view%20into%20the%20realities%20of%20the%20new%20AI%20economy.%20Here%20are%20the%20highlights%20from%20our%20chat%2C%20edited%20for%20clarity%20and%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlistair%3A%20What%20did%20you%20think%20you%20were%20signing%20up%20for%20when%20you%20first%20chose%20computer%20science%20as%20a%20degree%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKiran%3A%20After%20getting%20into%20UC%20Irvine%20in%202020%2C%20I%20took%20my%20first%20coding%20class%20and%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20it.%20The%20prospects%20at%20this%20time%20were%20that%20people%20were%20going%20into%20this%20major%20to%20get%20great%20jobs%20and%20it%20was%20very%20rewarding%20and%20I%20ended%20up%20liking%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20you%20believe%20a%20career%20in%20computer%20science%20would%20give%20you%20financially%2C%20socially%2C%20and%20emotionally%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dream%20at%20the%20time%20was%20definitely%20everyone%20was%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20go%20work%20for%20Google%20and%20the%20FAANG%20companies%20and%20get%20a%20six-figure%20salary.%26quot%3B%20My%20motivation%20was%20just%20getting%20a%20stable%20job%2C%20getting%20enough%20money%20to%20take%20care%20of%20my%20family%20%E2%80%94%20what%20everyone%20wants.%20I%20expected%20that%20computer%20science%20would%20put%20me%20in%20a%20position%20to%20grow%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%2C%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20and%20then%20maybe%20take%20me%20to%20more%20of%20the%20strategic%20side%2C%20the%20management%20side.%20The%20main%20thing%20that%20I%20did%20figure%20out%20was%20that%20I%20wanted%20financial%20stability%20and%20maybe%20financial%20independence%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFast%20forward%20to%20late%202022%2C%20when%20ChatGPT%20launched.%20Did%20you%20see%20that%20as%20a%20tool%20at%20the%20time%20or%20a%20threat%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20hater%20at%20the%20beginning.%20Then%2C%20friends%20of%20mine%20started%20using%20ChatGPT%20and%20they're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20you%20can%20just%20use%20it%20like%20Google.%20You%20can%20just%20text%20it%20and%20it'll%20give%20you%20the%20answer.%26quot%3B%20And%20honestly%2C%20my%20first%20thought%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20bit%20lazy.%20You%20can%20get%20more%20learning%20out%20of%20doing%20the%20work%20yourself.%26quot%3B%20But%20the%20more%20time%20went%20on%2C%20the%20more%20that%20people%20were%20using%20it%2C%20and%20they%20started%20using%20it%20for%20class.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20was%20ahead%20in%20class.%20I%20was%20doing%20the%20assignments%20well%20and%20understanding%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20there%20a%20moment%20when%20you%20thought%20generative%20AI%20might%20reduce%20the%20need%20for%20junior%20engineers%2C%20or%20do%20you%20even%20believe%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20know%20the%20current%20job%20market.%20It's%20not%20too%20hot%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20companies%20are%20citing%20AI%20as%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20for%20layoffs%20%E2%80%94%20but%20maybe%20that%20they%20were%20going%20to%20cut%20those%20jobs%20anyway.%20At%20the%20time%20though%2C%20while%20I%20was%20in%20school%20and%20using%20ChatGPT%2C%20I%20honestly%20didn't%20think%20it%20would%20get%20this%20far.%20I%20expected%20AI%20would%20be%20integrated%20into%20software%20engineers'%20work%20and%20companies%20would%20start%20integrating%20it%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20realize%20there%20would%20be%20potential%20for%20it%20to%20take%20over%20jobs%20that%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20I%20was%20very%20attentive%20to%20the%20job%20market%20situation%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20really%20thinking%20that%20far%20ahead.%20More%20of%20my%20worries%20at%20the%20time%20were%20just%20getting%20that%20first%20entry-level%20position.%20And%20I%20just%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20simple%3A%20I%20just%20get%20my%20degree%20and%20I%20would%20find%20a%20company%20that's%20hiring.%20Looking%20back%2C%20it%20was%20my%20mistake%20to%20not%20really%20research%20the%20current%20job%20market%20and%20maybe%20what%20some%20people%20were%20predicting%20about%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20didn't%20see%20it%20coming%20either.%20Few%20people%20did.%20Anyway%2C%20describe%20the%20moment%20when%20you%20realized%20the%20job%20market%20had%20changed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20already%20graduating%2C%20so%20this%20was%20after%20June%202025.%20I%20was%20getting%20into%20the%20reality%20of%20having%20to%20find%20my%20first%20job%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20I%20definitely%20started%20noticing%20something%20was%20wrong.%20A%20lot%20of%20my%20classmates%2C%20I%20haven't%20really%20heard%20of%20them%20getting%20any%20opportunities.%20Everyone's%20submitting%20so%20many%20resumes%20and%20there's%20a%20race%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20enhance%20resumes%20and%20send%20them%20out%20as%20fast%20as%20you%20can.%20And%20it%20seemed%20a%20lot%20more%20intense%20than%20I%20was%20prepared%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20my%20classmates%20and%20even%20students%20I%20know%20who%20are%20still%20in%20school%20are%20not%20even%20landing%20internships%20right%20now.%20It's%20not%20looking%20great.%20It's%20a%20very%20tough%20battle%20right%20now.%20So%20many%20people%20are%20quitting%20or%20getting%20fired%20or%20pivoting%20and%20there's%20new%20grads.%20Everyone%20is%20bracing%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20bloodbath%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20feel%20like%20you're%20competing%20against%20AI%20or%20laid-off%20senior%20engineers%20or%20both%2C%20or%20something%20else%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20fight%20is%20definitely%20with%20AI%20and%20all%20the%20competition%20with%20entry-level%20graduates%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20because%20AI%20is%20known%20to%20take%20over%20more%20junior%20roles.%20So%20it's%20important%20that%20we%20stay%20more%20relevant%20and%20offer%20something%20that%20AI%20can't.%20Scrolling%20through%20LinkedIn%20and%20on%20my%20job%20portals%2C%20I%20see%20more%20offers%20for%20mid-level%20positions%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20as%20many%20for%20entry-level%20roles.%20So%20it's%20like%20I'm%20fighting%20AI%20and%20all%20these%20other%20graduates%20for%20roles%20that%20don't%20exist%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20job%20search%20so%20far%2C%20what%20has%20it%20done%20to%20your%20confidence%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20be%20optimistic.%20I%20am%20lucky%20to%20have%20a%20better%20situation%20than%20some%20other%20people%20do.%20I'm%20living%20at%20home%20with%20family%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20as%20much%20about%20expenses.%20Still%2C%20if%20I%20weren't%20doing%20anything%20about%20my%20situation%2C%20I%20would%20feel%20pretty%20bummed.%20I'd%20feel%20kind%20of%20trapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I've%20been%20trying%20to%20work%20on%20building%20my%20network%2C%20finding%20people%20I%20know%20and%20learning%20from%20other%20people%2C%20just%20finding%20communities%20to%20be%20involved%20with.%20That's%20really%20helped%20my%20confidence%20because%20I%20find%20professionals%20that%20are%20trying%20to%20help%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20job%20market%20and%20they%20know%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20get%20that%20first%20job.%20The%20one%20saving%20grace%20in%20this%20tough%20situation%20is%20definitely%20the%20community%20I've%20found%20and%20the%20people%20I%20know%20who%20are%20helping%20me%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20you%20ever%20question%20your%20decision%20to%20study%20computer%20science%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20did%20question%20it.%20But%20I%20remember%20that%20I%20do%20like%20computer%20science%20and%20I%20did%20like%20what%20I%20learned.%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20my%20classes%20and%20programming.%20And%20instead%20of%20turning%20to%20a%20new%20discipline%2C%20I%20think%20I%20prefer%20to%20just%20specialize%20and%20find%20out%20new%20information%20and%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20news.%20And%20like%20I%20said%2C%20offer%20something%20that%20AI%20can't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20feel%20like%20you%20were%20trained%20for%20a%20version%20of%20the%20tech%20industry%20that%20no%20longer%20exists%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20a%20little%20salty%2C%20about%20this%2C%20if%20that's%20the%20right%20word.%20During%20my%20time%20at%20school%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20the%20degree%20was%20about%20was%20learning%20the%20basics%20of%20software%20engineering.%20You%20learn%20programming%20languages%20and%20you%20learn%20how%20to%20set%20up%20your%20development%20and%20deployment.%20But%20right%20now%20there%20are%20so%20many%20more%20tools%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20constant%20thing%20with%20the%20software%20engineering%20and%20the%20tech%20industry.%20There's%20always%20new%20technology%20and%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20up%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20AI%20in%20particular%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20graduated%20a%20bit%20too%20early.%20Because%20now%20AI%20will%20probably%20be%20more%20integrated%20into%20learning.%20I%20had%20so%20many%20professors%20that%20were%20more%20welcoming%20towards%20AI.%20I%20remember%20a%20really%20cool%20professor%20who%20shared%20a%20website%20that%20would%20let%20you%20make%20your%20own%20LLM.%20And%20it's%20really%20useful%20stuff%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum.%20It%20will%20be%20now%2C%20but%20I%20won't%20be%20there%20to%20see%20that%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I'm%20doing%20to%20help%20with%20that%2C%20and%20make%20the%20amends%2C%20is%20volunteering%20and%20doing%20more%20work%20on%20the%20side%20that%20involves%20newer%20technologies%20to%20just%20stay%20fresh%20and%20relevant%20and%20use%20all%20these%20new%20AI%20tools%20and%20see%20how%20I%20can%20leverage%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20a%20high%20school%20senior%20asked%20you%20today%20whether%20they%20should%20major%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20what%20would%20you%20tell%20them%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20depends%20on%20what%20interests%20them%20about%20computer%20science.%20If%20it's%20absolutely%20something%20they're%20interested%2C%20they%20love%20learning%20about%20the%20technology%20and%20they%20want%20to%20code%2C%20I%20would%20still%20say%20go%20for%20it%2C%20but%20I%20would%20recommend%20how%20to%20position%20yourself%20for%20after%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20start%20much%20earlier%20now%2C%20networking%20and%20knowing%20how%20to%20speak%20with%20people%20and%20how%20to%20apply%2C%20how%20to%20write%20a%20resume.%20And%20those%20all%20are%20also%20much%20more%20important%20now%20at%20the%20start%20of%20college%2C%20especially%20getting%20internships%2C%20if%20at%20all%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20would%20definitely%20recommend%20studying%20computer%20science%2C%20but%20being%20realistic%20about%20the%20opportunities%20available%20and%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20news%20and%20the%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20would%20you%20say%20to%20potential%20employers%20out%20there%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20should%20still%20be%20in%20hiring%20entry-level%20talent%20if%20possible.%20I%20know%20it's%20tough%20with%20the%20current%20market%20and%20the%20economy%20and%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20world%20right%20now.%20But%20entry-level%20talent%20is%20still%20important%20because%20you%20need%20to%20build%20this%20generation%20of%20professionals%20so%20that%20the%20future%20will%20have%20people%20to%20rely%20on.%20AI%20is%20still%20uncertain%20right%20now.%20People%20are%20still%20figuring%20out%20how%20it%20is%20impactful%20and%20it%20doesn't%20help%20to%20just%20force%20it%20upon%20your%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomputer-science-graduate-stability-ai-coding-tech-jobs-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773423400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b44a76a7a4f9df67ba4fc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomputer-science-graduate-stability-ai-coding-tech-jobs-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20a%20degree%20and%20skills%2C%20a%20new%20grad%20faces%20hiring%20challenges%20in%20tech%20due%20to%20AI's%20influence%20on%20entry-level%20job%20availability.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomputer-science-graduate-stability-ai-coding-tech-jobs-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22