22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20of%20my%20sons%20are%20enrolled%20in%20an%20international%20school%20in%20Las%20Rozas.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Cretella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20sold%20our%20house%20in%20the%20US%20and%20moved%20our%20four-person%20family%20to%20a%20suburb%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-american-family-made-moving-to-the-netherlands-leaving-us-2026-2%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emade%20some%20mistakes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20not%20translating%20important%20documents%20and%20canceling%20our%20US%20phone%20numbers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EErrors%20aside%2C%20I'm%20thrilled%20to%20be%20building%20a%20life%20for%20my%20family%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20our%20four-person%20family%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-spain-without-knowing-spanish-challenging-good-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20to%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20had%20roughly%20two%20semesters%20of%20college%20Spanish%20between%20us%20and%20zero%20experience%20living%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20let%20that%20stop%20us%2C%20though.%20Beginning%20in%20March%202025%2C%20we%20researched%20obsessively%2C%20read%20books%2C%20made%20spreadsheets%2C%20and%20put%20together%20lists%20of%20pros%20and%20cons.%20The%20more%20research%20we%20did%2C%20the%20more%20confident%20we%20became%20that%20Spain%20was%20the%20correct%20place%20for%20our%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20months%20later%2C%20we%20packed%20up%20our%20lives%20and%20moved%20our%206-%20and%209-year-old%20sons%20from%20Northford%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20to%20Las%20Rozas%20de%20Madrid%2C%20a%20suburb%20northwest%20of%20the%20Spanish%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20our%20extensive%20preparation%2C%20lessons%20awaited%20us.%20After%20all%2C%20there's%20so%20much%20to%20consider%20while%20moving%20abroad%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpros-and-cons-raising-children-abroad-spain-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eespecially%20with%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20slipups%20are%20unavoidable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20here%20are%20five%20mistakes%20I%20wish%20I'd%20avoided%20when%20my%20family%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287661b78-8e62-4eec-888d-8f7429c3b0ce%5C%22%3EI%20wish%20I'd%20started%20building%20my%20community%20abroad%20before%20we%20left%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20selling%20our%20home%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20finding%20a%20place%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-usa-to-spain-tried-multiple-cities-barcelona-madrid-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20in%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20figuring%20out%20where%20our%20sons%20would%20enroll%20in%20school%2C%20I%20deprioritized%20my%20new%20social%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20assumed%20we'd%20naturally%20meet%20people%20once%20we%20got%20here%2C%20and%20we%20eventually%20did.%20But%20those%20first%20few%20months%20were%20lonely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20arrived%20in%20August%2C%20a%20month%20before%20my%20sons'%20school%20year%20started%2C%20and%20many%20locals%20were%20still%20away%20on%20summer%20trips.%20Once%20school%20started%2C%20it%20became%20easier%20to%20connect%20with%20other%20families.%20I%20also%20joined%20a%20few%20WhatsApp%20groups%20recommended%20to%20me%20by%20other%20expats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20very%20much%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-friends-as-an-adult-living-abroad-home-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20a%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20here.%20If%20I%20were%20doing%20the%20move%20over%2C%20I'd%20join%20related%20regional%20and%20professional%20groups%2C%20connect%20with%20families%20in%20our%20area%2C%20and%20start%20building%20relationships%20before%20I%20even%20left%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20even%20one%20friend%20waiting%20for%20me%20in%20Spain%20would've%20made%20a%20huge%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b4774dd-9a0d-4edf-84bb-be8c0db6e44f%5C%22%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20didn't%20ask%20the%20right%20questions%20about%20our%20sons'%20school%20curricula%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rebecca%20Cretella%20and%20her%20family%20in%20Spain%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aebfedfd4fbd083f29bf24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20family%20relocated%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Spain%20in%202025.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Cretella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20planned%20to%20start%20our%20boys%20in%20an%20international%20school%20to%20ease%20their%20transition%20into%20a%20new%20country%20and%20language%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20eventually%20moving%20them%20into%20a%20local%20Spanish%20school%20once%20they%20were%20fluent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20selected%20an%20international%20private%20school%20that%20follows%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternational-baccalaureate-enrolled-american-program-uk-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInternational%20Baccalaureate%20(IB)%20curriculum%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Spanish%20language%20support.%20It%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20fit%20%E2%80%94%20until%20we%20realized%20we%20hadn't%20asked%20the%20right%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20failed%20to%20realize%20that%20our%20boys%2C%20who%20didn't%20arrive%20speaking%20Spanish%2C%20would%20be%20learning%20alongside%20native%20speakers%20rather%20than%20building%20introductory%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20getting%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fschool-in-spain-vs-us-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincredible%20education%20in%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20foundational%20language%20curriculum%20we%20expected.%20We%20now%20supplement%20school%20with%20online%20Spanish%20tutoring%20twice%20a%20week%20to%20fill%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20other%20parents%20moving%20their%20school-age%20kids%20abroad%20to%20Spain%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20asking%20specifically%20about%20language%20use%20and%20requesting%20sample%20lesson%20plans%20before%20enrolling%20to%20see%20what%20language%20support%20looks%20like%20in%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231f0a615-7efe-4119-8c1a-6057047eea15%5C%22%3ETranslating%20important%20documents%20into%20the%20local%20language%20would've%20been%20extremely%20helpful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20months%20after%20moving%2C%20I%20had%20to%20undergo%20emergency%20surgery.%20I%20felt%20completely%20unprepared%20as%20I%20relied%20on%20Google%20Translate%20and%20my%20husband's%20elementary%20Spanish%20language%20skills%20to%20communicate%20with%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20through%20it%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20through%20it%26quot%3B%20isn't%20the%20same%20as%20feeling%20safe%2C%20understood%2C%20and%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscary-er-visit-us-healthcare-fly-to-portugal-once-year-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escariest%20moment%20in%20the%20ER%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20right%20before%20I%20went%20under%20anesthesia.%20I%20was%20crying%20because%20I%20couldn't%20understand%20what%20the%20professionals%20were%20saying%2C%20couldn't%20communicate%20my%20allergies%20or%20medical%20history%2C%20and%20didn't%20know%20what%20was%20about%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20the%20staff%20took%20good%20care%20of%20me%2C%20but%20the%20experience%20was%20harder%20and%20more%20frightening%20than%20it%20needed%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20left%20the%20US%2C%20I%20should%20have%20saved%20a%20translated%20medical%20profile%20with%20my%20allergies%2C%20medications%2C%20and%20past%20surgeries%20on%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20should've%20researched%20how%20to%20access%20medical%20translation%20services%2C%20so%20that%20if%20something%20unexpected%20happens%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20figure%20it%20out%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc6ff299-2bdb-451e-93a9-d603998b17b3%5C%22%3EWe%20didn't%20know%20that%20we%20couldn't%20rent%20a%20car%20without%20a%20special%20driving%20permit%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rebecca%20Cretella%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20Spain%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af025f168b545ac9a6c49b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20few%20months%20living%20abroad%20were%20lonely%2C%20as%20we%20arrived%20without%20an%20established%20network.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Cretella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELas%20Rozas%20de%20Madrid%20is%20well-connected%2C%20so%20my%20family%20doesn't%20own%20a%20car%20here.%20When%20we%20went%20to%20rent%20one%20for%20a%20holiday%20trip%20to%20C%C3%A1diz%2C%20we%20assumed%20we%20could%20do%20so%20using%20our%20US%20driver's%20licenses%2C%20but%20we%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20an%20International%20Driving%20Permit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frenting-an-electric-car-italy-learning-curve-mistake-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erenting%20a%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20off%20the%20table.%20We%20made%20the%20best%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20but%20we%20were%20restricted%20in%20what%20we%20could%20see%20and%20do%20in%20C%C3%A1diz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20regret%20not%20getting%20an%20International%20Driving%20Permit%20before%20leaving%20the%20US.%20It's%20easy%20and%20costs%20%2420.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b3afd3a-1d01-404c-afc9-59f78c289413%5C%22%3ECanceling%20our%20US%20numbers%20created%20a%20logistical%20nightmare%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%2