inues%20to%20upend%20financial%20markets%20nearly%20two%20weeks%20after%20it%20began%2C%20and%20investors%20are%20seeking%20out%20safety%20trades%20amid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-energy-economist-iran-conflict-global-economy-trump-markets-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20soaring%20volatility%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJitania%20Kandhari%2C%20deputy%20CIO%20of%20the%20solutions%20and%20multi-asset%20group%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%20Investment%20Management%2C%20said%20that%20there's%20a%20key%20opportunity%20emerging%20that%20investors%20should%20consider.%20Kandhari%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20energy%20security%20is%20the%20trade%20to%20watch%20during%20the%20conflict%20and%20beyond.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20every%20country%20will%20want%20to%20have%20a%20very%20secure%20energy%20supply%2C%20energy%20resources%2C%20less%20dependence%20globally%2C%20just%20like%20we%20saw%20in%20this%20whole%20resource%20security%20that%20underpins%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20global%20power%20dynamics%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20view%20has%20recently%20informed%20her%20team's%20investment%20strategy.%20Kandhari%20added%20that%20they%20have%20been%20focused%20on%20geopolitical%20hedges%2C%20such%20as%20defense%20and%20energy%20stocks%20primed%20to%20gain%20amid%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20she%20also%20said%20that%20recently%2C%20the%20team%20has%20incrementally%20increased%20exposure%20to%20energy%20security%20and%20production.%20They%20see%20a%20shifting%20geopolitical%20landscape%20in%20which%20major%20economies%20are%20likely%20to%20rethink%20their%20energy%20needs%20and%20how%20they%20are%20secured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20one%20thing%20that%20we%20really%20think%20will%20emerge%20out%20of%20this%20is%20the%20whole%20energy%20supply%20chain%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20what%20that%20means%20for%20renewables%20%E2%80%94%20governments%20putting%20in%20favorable%20policies%2C%20be%20it%20subsidies%20or%20tax%20benefits%20for%20energy%20self-sufficiency%2C%20in%20whatever%20way%20possible%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKandhari%20sees%20the%20most%20opportunity%20within%20this%20new%20boom%20in%20the%20energy%20security%20supply%20chain.%20She%20highlighted%20several%20critical%20metals%20as%20likely%20beneficiaries.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20structural%20basis%2C%20we%20have%20also%20been%20invested%20in%20some%20of%20these%20commodities%2C%20copper%20or%20Uranium%2C%20which%20is%20needed%20for%20nuclear%20facilities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20countries%20increase%20their%20investments%20in%20energy%20security%2C%20Kandhari%20thinks%20they%20may%20double%20down%20on%20safety%20infrastructure.%20She%20added%20that%20this%20may%20create%20opportunities%20for%20companies%20in%20the%20defense%20and%20cybersecurity%20spaces%2C%20citing%20the%20likely%20need%20for%20guardrails%20as%20countries%20prioritize%20energy%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20she%20sees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-clean-energy-stock-picks-myrg-rxrx-fslr-solar-renewables-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%20investments%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20ways%20for%20investors%20to%20capitalize%20on%20a%20new%20phase%20of%20the%20energy%20narrative%2C%20even%20as%20markets%20focus%20heavily%20on%20oil%20flows%20due%20to%20the%20conflict.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRenewables%20is%20one%20way%20to%20play%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20some%20countries%20may%20also%20invest%2C%20or%20enable%20and%20promote%20investments%2C%20in%20refining%20capacity.%20I%20think%20there%20are%20opportunities%20that%20we%20have%20to%20look%20at%20it%20country%20by%20country%20to%20see%20where%20all%20of%20this%20looks%20interesting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%2