als-deal-sergio-gor-126031301190_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fus-india-moving-close-to-finalising-critical-minerals-deal-sergio-gor-126031301190_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20attended%20a%20weekend%20reading%20retreat%20in%20my%2060s.%20Surrounded%20by%20women%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20I%20learned%20more%20than%20I'd%20ever%20imagined.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20with%20hat%20and%20jacket%20on%20smiling%20amid%20trees%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a741f8fd4fbd083f29744e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20weekend%20spent%20with%20strangers%20yielded%20wonderful%20memories%20and%20valuable%20lessons.%20%3Cp%3ESandra%20Gordon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20the%20weekend%20reading%20retreat%20I%20attended%2C%20our%20intergenerational%20group%20bonded%20over%20more%20than%20books.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20had%20thoughtful%20discussions%2C%20did%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-meditate%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eguided%20meditation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20went%20on%20a%20hike%20in%20the%20woods.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20came%20home%20inspired%20by%20the%20other%20retreat%20members%20and%20our%20shared%20connection.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%2030s%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-neighborhood-book-club-to-make-real-friends-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejoined%20a%20book%20club%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20soon%20dropped%20out.%20Between%20juggling%20work%20and%20family%2C%20the%20last%20thing%20I%20needed%20then%20was%20another%20deadline%2C%20even%20a%20read-for-fun%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlash%20forward%20decades%3A%20I'm%20in%20my%2060s%20now%2C%20the%20kids%20have%20flown%20the%20nest%2C%20and%20I%20have%20more%20downtime%20and%20love%20all%20things%20outdoorsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20a%20friend%20suggested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allbookedretreats.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAll%20Booked%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20luxe%20reading%20retreat%20for%20women%20in%20New%20York%20State's%20Catskill%20Mountains%2C%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20try%20book%20clubs%20again%2C%20especially%20this%20one-off%20weekend%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20signed%20up%2C%20I%20imagined%20lengthy%20chats%20surrounding%20the%20retreat's%20featured%20trending%20book%3A%20%26quot%3BMother%20Mary%20Come%20to%20Me%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20memoir%20by%20prize-winning%20author%20Arundhati%20Roy%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EWe%20certainly%20had%20those.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20made%20the%20literary%20getaway%20especially%20meaningful%20were%20the%20casual%20connections%20we%20shared%20as%20total%20strangers%20%E2%80%94%20eight%20women%20in%20our%2020s%20to%20late%2060s%20%E2%80%94%20about%20life%2C%20love%2C%20and%20living%20with%20intention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220347046e-53dd-41a1-a65a-9a66730a4a8b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20retreat's%20luxe%20cabin%20was%20the%20perfect%20place%20for%20book%20chats%20and%20a%20reset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Exterior%20of%20a%20log%20cabin%20with%20bushes%20in%20front%20of%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a7424ffd4fbd083f29745d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20weekend%20retreat%20offered%20amenities%2C%20including%20a%20guided%20meditation%20and%20a%20hike%20in%20a%20gorgeous%20getaway-from-it-all%20location.%3Cp%3ESandra%20Gordon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETucked%20among%2012%20wooded%20acres%20in%20Windham%2C%20New%20York%2C%20the%20weekend%20retreat's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F9-enormous-log-cabin-mansions-for-sale-2015-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eluxury%20log%20cabin%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20straight%20out%20of%20Airbnb%20central%20casting%2C%20complete%20with%20pine%20exposed%20beams%2C%20stone%20floors%2C%20and%20a%20dramatic%20great%20room%20with%20soaring%20vaulted%20ceilings%20and%20cozy%20reading%20nooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20night%2C%20we%20met%20our%20host%2C%20Suzanne%2C%20a%20former%20New%20York%20City%20journalist%20who%20headed%20to%20the%20Catskills%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20and%20never%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20introduced%20ourselves%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F25-books-jeff-bezos-elon-musk-bill-gates-loved-read-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efavorite%20book%20recommendation%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20an%20Indian-inspired%20dinner%20of%20delicata-squash%20salad%20and%20curry-marinated%20chicken%2C%20a%20nod%20to%20featured%20author%20Roy%2C%20who%20calls%20New%20Delhi%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20changing%20into%20our%20PJs%2C%20we%20gathered%20on%20yoga%20mats%20in%20the%20cabin's%20loft%20for%20a%20guided%20meditation%20before%20padding%20off%20to%20our%20log%20beds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20beds%20in%20room%20of%20cabin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a7424ffd4fbd083f29745b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20slept%20in%20cozy%20beds.%3Cp%3ESandra%20Gordon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIntroductions%20continued%20the%20next%20morning%20over%20a%20breakfast%20of%20blueberry%20scones%20and%20homemade%20granola.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20us%20were%20two%2020-something%20bookstagrammers%2C%20each%20with%20her%20own%20daunting%20stack%20of%20extracurricular%20romantasy%20novels%20to%20speed-read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20tripods%20and%20ring%20lights%20triggered%20the%20multitasking%20question%20that%20seemed%20to%20trail%20many%20of%20us%20these%20days%20wherever%20we%20went%3A%20Should%20we%20turn%20an%20experience%20into%20shareable%20content%20or%20power%20down%20and%20just%20enjoy%20it%2C%20conceivably%20leaving%20likes%2C%20followers%2C%20and%20revenue%20(from%20somewhere)%20on%20the%20table%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20planning%20to%20snap%20a%20few%20photos%2C%20I%20am%20Team%20Commune%20with%20Nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de0c5646-f78b-4e81-82c9-c4cee32ce1b3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20multigenerational%20group%20bonded%20over%20books%2C%20nature%2C%20and%20a%20lively%20debate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wood%20table%20with%20books%20on%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a7424f1fb3fcb42648d980%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20trip%20consisted%20of%20more%20than%20just%20reading.%20%3Cp%3ESandra%20Gordon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20morning%20of%20quiet%20reading%20time%2C%20our%20group%20met%20at%20the%20Windham%20Path%20for%20an%20afternoon%20of%20forest%20bathing%2C%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20slow-motion%20hike%20led%20by%20Beth%2C%20our%20certified%20forest%20therapy%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeth%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-properly-quit-your-job-employee-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleft%20a%20corporate%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20embrace%20her%20calling%20as%20a%20forest%20therapist%2C%20invited%20us%20to%20wander%20off%20and%20%26quot%3Bconnect%20with%20a%20tree%20you%20are%20drawn%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20appreciating%20the%20bark%2C%20treetops%2C%20and%20stillness%2C%20we%20reunited%20with%20a%20tea%20ceremony.%20Beth%20poured%20tiny%20cups%20of%20tea%20steeped%20from%20pine%20needles%20from%20an%20insulated%20kettle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20sipping%20the%20sour%20reddish%20liquid%2C%20we%20were%20inst