0empty%20nester%2C%20I%20often%20feel%20%3Cem%3Enestless.%3C%2Fem%3E%20It's%20almost%20like%20I'm%20back%20in%20my%2020s%2C%20asking%20fundamental%20questions%20again%2C%20such%20as%3A%20What%20should%20I%20do%20now%3F%20Where%20should%20I%20live%20now%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20tied%20to%20a%20good%20school%20system%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20spending%20the%20weekend%20with%20retreat%20members%2C%20including%20Suzanne%20and%20forest-bathing%20Beth%2C%20who've%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-us-to-buy-farmhouse-in-france-after-divorce-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebold%20midlife%20moves%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reminded%20me%20that%20life%20is%20an%20open%20book%2C%20filled%20with%20exciting%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20I've%20been%20really%20noticing%20the%20trees%20during%20my%20daily%20walks%2C%20brushing%20up%20on%20my%20vlogging%20skills%20(inspired%20by%20the%20bookstagrammers'%20industriousness)%2C%20and%20seeking%20out%20even%20more%20ways%20to%20meet%20new%20friends%20of%20all%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweekend-retreat-women-of-all-ages-life-lessons-catskillls-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773418741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a741f8fd4fbd083f29744e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweekend-retreat-women-of-all-ages-life-lessons-catskillls-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Attending%20All%20Booked%2C%20a%20women's%20weekend%20reading%20retreat%20in%20the%20Catskills%2C%20helped%20me%20make%20new%20friends%20and%20learn%20meaningful%20lessons%20about%20life%20and%20love.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sandra%20Gordon)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweekend-retreat-women-of-all-ages-life-lessons-catskillls-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alex%20Karp%20says%20AI%20is%20bad%20news%20for%20'humanities-trained%2C%20largely%20Democratic%20voters'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Karp%20speaks%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b42cb6a96e437d6eb84618%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalantir%20CEO%20Alex%20Karp%20said%20AI%20is%20so%20disruptive%20that%20only%20national%20security%20concerns%20justify%20pursuing%20the%20breakthrough%20technology.%3Cp%3EMarkus%20Schreiber%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPalantir%20CEO%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falex-karp-bio-palantir-ceo%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Alex%20Karp%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20even%20people%20in%20his%20industry%20don't%20appreciate%20how%20disruptive%20AI%20will%20be.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKarp%20said%20that%20AI%20job%20losses%20will%20also%20alter%20the%20American%20political%20landscape.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20US%20isn't%20careful%2C%20he%20said%2C%20there%20will%20be%20an%20outpouring%20of%20hatred%20for%20%26quot%3Brich%20people%20in%20tech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-cto-shyam-sankar-leadership-tips-top-employees-mistakes-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPalantir%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20Alex%20Karp%20says%20AI%20will%20upend%20society%20and%20that%20even%20people%20in%20tech%20underestimate%20%26quot%3Bhow%20disruptive%20these%20technologies%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20going%20to%20disrupt%20the%20economic%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20political%20power%20significantly%20of%20one%20party's%20base%2C%20highly%20educated%2C%20often%20female%20voters%20who%20vote%20mostly%20Democrat%2C%20and%20military%20and%20working%20class%20people%20who%20do%20not%20feel%20supported%2C%20and%20you%20feel%20like%20that's%2C%20you%20believe%20that%20that's%20going%20to%20work%20out%20politically%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20in%20an%20insane%20asylum%2C%26quot%3B%20Karp%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Thursday%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20AIPCon%209%20in%20Maryland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarp%20said%20that%2C%20since%20AI%20will%20largely%20disrupt%20white-collar%20work%2C%20it%20will%20place%20greater%20value%20on%20vocational%20skills%2C%20upending%20the%20political%20paradigms%20of%20the%20Trump%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20technology%20disrupts%20humanites%20trained%2C%20largely%20Democratic%20voters%2C%20and%20makes%20their%20economic%20power%20less%2C%20and%20increases%20the%20power%2C%20economic%20power%2C%20vocationally%20trained%2C%20working%20class%2C%20often%20male%20voters%2C%20and%2C%20and%2C%20and%20so%2C%20these%20disruptions%20are%20going%20to%20disrupt%20every%20aspect%20of%20our%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudies%20show%20that%20many%20white-collar%20fields%20are%20the%20most%20exposed%20to%20the%20initial%20wave%20of%20AI-related%20disruption.%20Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20has%20warned%20that%20AI%20could%20wipe%20out%20up%20to%20half%20of%20all%20white-collar%2C%20entry-level%20jobs%20over%20the%20next%201%20to%205%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarp%20has%20long%20positioned%20himself%20and%20Palantir%20as%20champions%20of%20the%20working%20class%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20focus%20on%20the%20US%20military.%20He's%20declared%20the%20software%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-ceo-alex-karp-calls-company-anti-woke-revenue-surge-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bcompletely%20anti-woke%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20pushed%20back%20against%20employees%20who%20have%20questioned%20the%20firm's%20contracts%20with%20US%20immigration%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20can%20justify%20pursuing%20such%20a%20disruptive%20technology%20as%20AI%20only%20if%20it%20is%20coupled%20with%20national%20security%2C%20Karp%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20technologies%20are%20dangerous%20societally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20justification%20you%20could%20possibly%20have%20would%20be%20if%20we%20don't%20do%20it%2C%20our%20adversaries%20will%20do%20it%2C%20and%20we%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20their%20rule%20of%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Karp%20sketched%20out%20what%20could%20happen%20in%20a%20world%20that%20doesn't%20come%20together%20in%20the%20face%20of%20AI.%20In%20particular%2C%20he%20called%20for%20wholesale%20changes%20to%20the%20US%20education%20system%20to%20better%20prioritize%20skills-based%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%2C%20the%20danger%20is%20if%20we%20don't%20do%20these%20reforms%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20get%20the%20pitchforks%2C%20because%20then%20the%20only%20solution%20people%20are%20going%20to%20have%20is%2C%20well%2C%20let's%20go%20after%20the%20unlikeable%2C%20rich%20people%20in%20tech%2C%20especially%20AI%20tech%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20a%20recent%20interview%20on%20TBPN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3VIdkv3Kx48%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22FULL%20INTERVIEW%3A%20Alex%20Karp%20on%20AI%2C%20Job%20Loss%2C%20and%20the%20Future%20of%20Work%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Palantir%20has%20not%20disclosed%20why%2C%20the%20firm%20recently%20relocated%20from%20Colorado%2C%20a%20state%20that%20has%20become%20more%20Democratic%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20to%20Florida%2C%20where%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20has%20overseen%20an%20explosion%20in%20Republican%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarp%20contrasted%20the%20future%20of%20America%20with%20that%20of%20Germany%2C%20where%20he%20spent%20significant%20time%20pursuing%20a%20Ph.D%20at%20Goethe%20University%20in%20Frankfurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20like%20you%20guys%2C%20young%20people%20building%20things%20that%20feel%20hampered%20and%20are%20correct%20to%20feel%20hampered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20American%20version%2C%20if%20we're%20not%20careful%2C%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20the%20German%20version.%20I%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20be%2C%20'Hang%20the%20rich.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falex-karp-ai-job-displacement-humanities-democratic-voters-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773418354000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b42cc4a7a4f9df67ba4c38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falex-karp-ai-job-displacement-humanities-democratic-voters-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Palantir%20CEO%20Alex%20Karp%20said%20AI%20will%20lead%20to%20increase%20in%20political%20and%20economic%20power%20for%20the%20working%20class.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falex-karp-ai-job-displacement-humanities-democratic-voters-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20and%20allies%20fear%20easing%20Russian%20sanctions%20will%20prolong%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773418347000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Faf04%2Flive%2F899c8480-1eeb-11f1-8cb7-