%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faccenture-announces-new-leadership-for-reinvention-services-division-126031301167_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faccenture-announces-new-leadership-for-reinvention-services-division-126031301167_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faccenture-announces-new-leadership-for-reinvention-services-division-126031301167_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anthropic's%20top%20lawyer%20says%20AI%20will%20kill%20the%20legal%20profession's%20dreaded%20billable%20hour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223731%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jeff%20bleich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b385e6a7a4f9df67ba4728%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222487%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Bleich%2C%20now%20Anthropic's%20general%20counsel%2C%20thinks%20artificial%20intelligence%20will%20usher%20in%20the%20death%20of%20the%20billable%20hour%20business%20model%20for%20law%20firms.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Salangsang%2FVariety%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic's%20Jeff%20Bleich%20says%20AI%20will%20end%20the%20billable%20hour's%20dominance%20in%20legal%20billing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBillable%20hours%20mean%20lawyers%20get%20paid%20more%20when%20they%20spend%20more%20time%20on%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20AI%20tools%20eliminate%20%26quot%3Btedious%26quot%3B%20work%2C%20which%20devalues%20the%20time%20lawyers%20spend%20overall%2C%20Bleich%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billable%20hour's%20time%20is%20approaching%20midnight%2C%20according%20to%20Anthropic's%20top%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20the%20billable%20hour%20is%20the%20solution%2C%20and%20we've%20known%20it%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20Bleich%2C%20the%20AI%20company's%20general%20counsel%2C%20said%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20American%20Bar%20Association's%20White%20Collar%20Crime%20Institute%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20Bleich%20said%20that%20artificial%20intelligence%20tools%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-billable-hour-lawyers-legal-world-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeliminating%20the%20need%20for%20companies%20to%20hire%20armies%20of%20lawyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20do%20lucrative%20yet%20%26quot%3Btedious%26quot%3B%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we've%20got%20a%20technology%20that's%20going%20to%20eliminate%20the%20sorts%20of%20things%20that%20allow%20people%20to%20become%20wealthy%20off%20of%20tedious%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Bleich%20said%20on%20the%20panel%2C%20alongside%20top%20lawyers%20at%20Google%2C%20IBM%2C%20and%20Liberty%20Mutual.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20not%20what%20lawyers%20are%20trained%20to%20do%2C%20and%20not%20what%20we%20ultimately%20look%20to%20lawyers%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flexisnexis-ceo-predicts-ai-increase-lawyer-legal-fees-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emuch-maligned%20billable%20hour%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20standard%20method%20that%20law%20firms%20use%20to%20bill%20their%20clients.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20track%20the%20work%20done%20for%20each%20client%2C%20often%20in%20six-minute%20increments%2C%20tally%20them%20up%2C%20and%20charge%20their%20clients%20accordingly.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20billable%20hour%20has%20been%20useful%20to%20help%20companies%20and%20other%20clients%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-house-legal-tech-ai-cost-cutting-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunderstand%20what%20they%20are%20paying%20lawyers%20for%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20has%20also%20%26quot%3Bcreated%20a%20wedge%2C%26quot%3B%20Bleich%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20current%20system%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20interests%20of%20firms%20are%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20interests%20of%20their%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Companies%20want%20lawyers%20to%20resolve%20problems%20quickly%2C%20but%20law%20firms%20get%20paid%20more%20when%20the%20work%20takes%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClients%20want%20you%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20as%20efficiently%20as%20possible%20and%20with%20as%20little%20drama%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Bleich%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you're%20a%20company%2C%20the%20bigger%20the%20case%20gets%2C%20and%20the%20more%20dramatic%20it%20gets%2C%20and%20the%20more%20complicated%20it%20gets%2C%20and%20the%20more%20work%20that%20has%20to%20be%20done%20%E2%80%94%20the%20more%20lucrative%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20panelists%20largely%20agreed%20with%20Bleich's%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20value%20is%20no%20longer%20you%20putting%20in%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Damon%20Hart%2C%20the%20top%20lawyer%20at%20Liberty%20Mutual.%20%26quot%3BThe%20value%20is%20your%20strategy%2C%20your%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnne%20Robinson%2C%20IBM's%20general%20counsel%2C%20told%20the%20audience%20that%20she's%20open%20to%20working%20with%20them%20to%20figure%20out%20more%20creative%20billing%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20open%20to%20firms%20coming%20and%20saying%2C%20'I'd%20really%20like%20to%20work%20with%20you%20on%20this%20matter%20or%20this%20type%20of%20work%2C%20I%20get%20that%20the%20billable%20hour%20model%20is%20not%20one%20of%20aligned%20incentives%2C%20and%20so%20let's%20sit%20down%20and%20talk%20about%20what%20you%20expect%20as%20far%20as%20outcomes%20and%20how%20we%20can%20both%20get%20there%20in%20a%20way%20that%20reflects%20your%20pressures%20and%20your%20priorities%2C'%26quot%3B%20Robinson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBleich%20said%20he%20still%20values%20the%20work%20of%20outside%20law%20firms%2C%20but%20wants%20them%20to%20find%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20billable%20hour%20that%20works%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20sort%20of%20cheap%20out%20and%20starve%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Bleich%20said.%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20you%20have%20to%20have%20an%20economic%20model%20that%20works.%20And%20the%20firms%20that%20adapt%20to%20that%20faster%20and%20better%20will%20be%20leapfrogging%20other%20firms%2C%20because%20they'll%20be%20more%20attractive%20to%20work%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBleich's%20comments%20come%20at%20a%20critical%20moment%20for%20Anthropic%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-sues-pentagon-lawsuit-supply-chain-risk-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esued%20federal%20agencies%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20Trump%20administration%20effectively%20blacklisted%20it%20following%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-backs-anthropic-pentagon-legal-fight-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecollapse%20of%20contract%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20Anthropic%20is%20represented%20by%20WilmerHale%2C%20one%20of%20the%20law%20firms%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-law-new-executive-order-wilmerhale-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump%20targeted%20last%20year%20with%20an%20executive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-executive-order-wilmerhale-big-law-unconstitutional-coercion-retaliation-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equickly%20blocked%20by%20a%20federal%20judge%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20firms%20that%20show%20some%20spine%2C%26quot%3B%20Bleich%20said%20following%20the%20panel%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20using%20law%20firms%20that%20fought%20back%20against%20Trump's%20executive%20orders%20targeting%20them.%20He%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20lawsuit%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilmerHale%20is%20distinguished%20in%20another%20way%3A%20Reginald%20Heber%20Smith%2C%20who%20in%20the%20early%2020th%20century%20managed%20the%20Big%20Law%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20then%20called%20Hale%20and%20Dorr%20%E2%80%94%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thomsonreuters.com%2Fen-us%2Fposts%2Flegal%2Fbillable-hour-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewidely%20credited%20with%20inventing%20the%20billable%20hour%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-general-counsel-jeff-bleich-ai-billable-hour-lawyers-ibm-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773415688000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b3860ba7a4f9df67ba472a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-general-counsel-jeff-bleich-ai-billable-hour-lawyers-ibm-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthropic%20Jeff%20Bleich%20told%20a%20room%20full%20of%20Big%20Law%20lawyers%20to%20rethink%20their%20approach%20to%20billing%20clients.%20Execs%20from%20other%20big%20companies%20agreed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-general-counsel-jeff-bleich-ai-billable-hour-lawyers-ibm-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Navy%20destroyers%20are%20firing%20top%20interceptors%20to%20bring%20down%20Iranian%20missiles%20flying%20into%20NATO%20airspace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Standard%20Missile%20-3%20Block%20IIA%2C%20or%20SM-3%20Blk%20IIA%2C%20is%20launched%20from%20US%20Navy%20Arleigh%20Burke-class%20guided%20missile%20destroyer%20USS%20McCampbell%20(DDG%2085)%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Missile%20Range%20Facility%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20during%20Flight%20Test%20Other-23%20or%20FTX-23%2C%20February%208%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b427aea7a4f9df67ba4b7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20Navy%20has%20used%20SM-3s%20on%20three%20occasions%20to%20defend%20Turkish%20airspace%20over%20the%20past%20two%20weeks.%3Cp%3EUS%20Missile%20Defense%20Agency%20photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20US%20Navy%20destroyer%20used%20an%20SM-3%20interceptor%20to%20down%20an%20Iranian%20ballistic%20missile%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20the%20third%20time%20in%20two%20weeks%20that%20a%20Navy%20destroyer%20used%20the%20SM-3%20to%20defend%20NATO%20airspace.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESM-3s%20are%20among%20are%20top%20missile%20interceptors%2C%20but%20they%20come%20with%20a%20hefty%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20destroyers%20operating%20in%20the%20Eastern%20Mediterranean%20Sea%20have%20been%20launching%20SM-3s%20%E2%80%94%20among%20America's%20most%20high-end%20interceptors%20%E2%80%94%20to%20defend%20NATO%20airspace%20against%20incoming%20Iranian%20ballistic%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20Arleigh%20Burke-class%20destroyer%20USS%20Oscar%20Austin%20fired%20at%20least%20one%20SM-3%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-top-interceptor-missile-heavy-price-tag-low-procurement-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStandard%20Missile-3%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20interceptor%20to%20bring%20down%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-higher-end-air-defenses-no-longer-factors-us-general-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIranian%20ballistic%20missile%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Turkish%20airspace%2C%20a%20defense%20official%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20marked%20the%20third%20time%20since%20February%