3%2Fvivek-menon-elephant-corridors-india-conservation-wildlife-trust-of-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Knocked%20on%20Every%20Door%E2%80%99%3A%20How%201%20Teacher%20Brought%20100%20Children%20Back%20to%20School%20in%20Raebareli%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sangeeta%20Maurya%20first%20received%20her%20posting%20in%20a%20small%20village%20school%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Raebareli%20district%2C%20she%20broke%20down%20in%20tears.%20Having%20cleared%20the%20challenging%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(UGC%20NET)%2C%20she%20had%20imagined%20herself%20in%20a%20well-equipped%20classroom%2C%20filled%20with%20eager%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20standing%20inside%20a%20crumbling%20building%20with%20broken%20benches%2C%20absent%20children%2C%20and%20silence%20that%20stretched%20down%20the%20dusty%20corridors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wondered%20if%20this%20was%20truly%20where%20her%20teaching%20journey%20would%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496794%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%2012%20years%20later%2C%20she%20smiles%20when%20she%20recalls%20that%20moment.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20stayed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20never%20have%20learnt%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3